NEW CUSTOM KITCHEN WITH ALL HARDWOODS AND QUARTZ COUNTERTOPS. WET BAR WITH NEW SINK AND CUSTOM FINISHES PERFECT FOR ENTERTAINING. ALL BATHROOMS REMODELED TO INCLUDE DUROCK, VALVE AND PLUMBING. HUGE MASTER BEDROOM OVERLOOKS THE LAKE. AC REPLACED IN 2017/NEW AC DUCTS  2021/NEW WASHER/DRYER 2018. THE PROPERTY SITS ACROSS FROM HILLSBORO PARK WHICH OFFERS BASKETBALL, VOLLEYBALL, 2 PICNIC PAVILLIONS, PICKLEBALL AND BIKE TRAILS. THIS IS TRULY THE BEST KEPT SECRET IN DEERFIELD. COME AND SEE THIS GORGEOUS ESTATE WITH VAULTED CEILINGS THAT AWAITS A NEW OWNER.
